data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom 3-bath 3-car garage beauty marks its fabulous 1-year old milestone.  Home is in the great neighborhood of Estancia West, located less than 4 miles from Fort Hood and even closer to schools.  This home is in pristine condition; granite counters in kitchen with center island, extensive cabinets, high ceilings, well-placed windows that maximize natural light, huge master bedroom with very spacious bathroom, and a Texas sized walk-in closet.  Enjoy cozy fall nights in-front of the large fireplace in the open floorplan living room.  New security system included with home, and much more. The exterior will relax you with its charming, covered patio, and fully fenced back yard.
